# Compiled manuscript PDFs — regenerable via `make pdf` / `make supplementary`.
# main.pdf AND supplementary.pdf are intentionally tracked so the latest
# manuscript and supplement are downloadable from the repo without a LaTeX
# toolchain; remember to rebuild both before committing.
